---
title: "Example: Coherence analysis"
author: "H. Matuschek"
date: 2020-02-20
---

```julia
using ContinuousWavelet
using Plots
gr();

N = 1024;
M = 64;
X = zeros(Float64, N, M);
#X[N÷2] = 1;
for i in 1:M
  X[:,i] = sin.(2π*(1:N)/50)
end

wt = WaveletTransform(CauchyWavelet(10.0), Array{Float64, 1}(LinRange(2,100, 64)));

Cx = coherence(wt, X)
Cs = coherence(wt, surrogate(X))
plot(
  contourf(Cx),
  contourf(Cs),
  layout=(2,1)
)
```
